{
  "stem": "20609.4",
  "chunk_idx": 17,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] In September 1950-- [LAUGHS] no, I got-- all of a sudden in July or August, the Korean War starts and I get a notice, greetings.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So I get nailed and I had to go to Charleston, West Virginia to-- to get my induction, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- and the minute you say, [LAUGHS] I'm Jewish, 1A.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] You could have flat feet, you can't hear, you're 1A.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean, I-- I-- so that's how I got into the army for two years, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Again, I was very fortunate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I took over an officers club while I was there because I had that background and I survived the-- the two years.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I didn't get sent overseas, although there was a number of times I was on orders.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But the colonel always took-- because I had a very essential job.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I made a profit for the club and that they never had before.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I cut out the dues, didn't have to pay dues.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I gave them free parties because I had a very corrupt [LAUGHS] mess officer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I hope the army doesn't nail me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But he-- he got nailed, I understand, because he-- they found out at a grocery store in Philadelphia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "His name was Captain Harvey, I'll never forget his name.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I became initially his personal cook.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I used to make him eggs Benedict and steaks Diane.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "This is what he-- you know, what I learned as a waiter, you know, and in those kind of places.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And so that was my tour in the army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And that's mois.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
